social_posts.post_text: Happy little Christmas shelfie 🎄🎅🏽
It’s been so hard keeping these cute faces private! We are so happy they are a part of our family ❤️ two cute nieces! Also a reason I hardly post photos of anything, they’re always in them! 🥰
One more sleep 🎄🎅🏼🎁 @kingofchristmas
I mean, Christmas break is almost over right?!?
Basketball season photo dump! My boy played so good today and they won 🏀 aunt meg surprised Max and brought the cousins to watch his game ❤️
My best boy is SIX today! He lights up every single part of our life! He’s funny and kind. Loves to fish, ride four wheelers and dirt bikes and baseball. I’m so proud that he is ours 🫶🏼
Rome Braves taking home a win ⚾️
Come unbox my @azariabrand order with me! I’ve been wanting a couple new bags to carry and these checked all the boxes! (You can use code MRSCOURTNEYCOOPER for a discount) 🥰👜 #azariaambassador
This was a season of massive growth for this kid! My little short stop. we also got to watch him hit his first home run ⚾️❤️⚾️
12 years of marriage❤️ thankful he chooses  to love me every day ❤️ thankful for the two cute kids we made ❤️ thankful that he leads our family ❤️ just really really grateful ❤️
Lake dump 🚤⛱️🌊
Hartwell 2023. The best 10 days of family time. Lots of fun and lots of kids!

One of my favorite places to sit and drink my morning coffee and read. We partnered with @homereserve on sprucing up a few spaces in our home and I’m obsessed with these chairs in our sitting room! They’re super comfy and spacious! Just like all of our home reserve pieces! Dolly especially loves when she gets to lay on the furniture 🥰
Not ready to say goodbye to warm weather 💓🌊💓

I read over 200 books this year but only 11 of the physical books made my 5⭐️ list.  Tell me what books I need to add to my 2024 list. I have a few historical fiction, memoirs, and romance added! I also can’t wait to read @kennedyryan1 sequel to Before I Let Go.

Family holiday photos loading 🌲🍂🍁 @dsw has the best selection of footwear from @heydude to complete any of your looks for the holidays! I’ve put together a collection of my favorites on LTK 🥰  @shop.ltk #mydsw #sponsored #liketkit shop our favs here: https://liketk.it/4nruZ
I’m not usually so behind on getting my tree put together but we went out of town for thanksgiving! Well, here she is! Still love her. Still love pink. @kingofchristmas
Happy Sunday and Merry Christmas (Eve) friends ❤️🎄 Love, The Coopers

2023 brought a lot of change. We made some difficult decisions and transitions that ultimately we knew were best for our family, we had a lot of fun, and we spent our days (that weren’t for work) on the lake, ball field, and the wrestling mats! Bring it on 2024 ❤️
